+        // The per-property encoders above now return RAW bytes; compress them
+        // here in parallel. Properties within a chunk are independent and the
+        // deflate compression is the single dominant cost of RAD encoding
+        // (callgrind on a 1.18M-splat file: compress_to_vec + flush_block ≈
+        // 28.6% of total instructions — larger than all the similarity FP math).
